com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message

Class MessageFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.neebal.android.simplyreliable.message.MessageFactory

  • public class MessageFactory
extends Object
    Represents a singleton factory instance that will be used to handle the creation/saving/destroying of the various OutMessage instances. It is to ensure that there are unique OutMessage instances in the API eco system.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Neebal Technologies
